<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Linear - Ecossistema Digital</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --black: #0a0a0a;
            --gold: #c5a059;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --gray: #1a1a1a;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Header e Animação Loop */
        .hero-section {
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #1a1a1a 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
            position: relative;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.2);
        }

        .lina-animation {
            width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid var(--gold);
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.3);
            object-fit: cover;
            /* O vídeo gerado acima deve ser colocado aqui */
        }

        /* Grid de Cards */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: -100px auto 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--gray);
            border: 1px solid #333;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--white);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .card i {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #aaa;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Video Player Section */
        .video-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background: var(--black);
        }

        .video-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 4px solid var(--gray);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        }

        video {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <video class="lina-animation" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
                <source src="URL_DO_VIDEO_GERADO_ACIMA" type="video/mp4">
            </video>
            <h1 style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 300;">Ecossistema Digital <span style="color: var(--gold);">Linear</span></h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <a href="https://nextrisedev.github.io/lina/" class="card" target="_blank">
            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
            <h3>Lina</h3>
            <p>Construtor de mensagens inteligente para otimização de comunicação.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://nextrisedev.github.io/linear/agendamentos" class="card" target="_blank">
            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
            <h3>Agendamentos</h3>
            <p>Gestão da semana - Unidade Loja Indianópolis.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://nextrisedev.github.io/linear/rotina_sugestiva.html" class="card" target="_blank">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            <h3>Time de Captação</h3>
            <p>Rotinas sugestivas e processos operacionais da equipe.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://nextrisedev.github.io/linear/main.html" class="card" target="_blank">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            <h3>Dashboard Executivo</h3>
            <p>Visão consolidada: Bruto x Líquido (Módulo em construção).</p>
        </a>
    </div>

    <section class="video-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Inovação em IA</h2>
        <div class="video-container">
            <video controls poster="Lina_Human.png">
                <source src="https://nextrisedev.github.io/linear/assets/Cria%C3%A7%C3%A3o_de_V%C3%ADdeo_Animado_para_IA.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Seu navegador não suporta vídeos.
            </video>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: #444; font-size: 0.8rem;">
        &copy; 2024 Linear AI Ecosystem - Sofisticação e Tecnologia.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
